	<p id="_f8a6654f-8be4-49ff-a9a5-85b7816a69f4">The JCTLM Secretariat has the responsibility and authority to receive, manage and transfer nominations of CRMs, RMM/Ps and RMSs and nominations for membership on JCTLM RTs to the JCTLM DB WG Chairs and RT Leaders.</p>
